1. Build custom ISO based on Ubuntu upstream mirror candidate.<br/>
2. Run tests for Ubuntu upstream mirrors candidate builded by<br>
<b><a href="http://osci-jenkins.srt.mirantis.net:8080/view/mirrors/job/mirrors-local-msk-ubuntu/">mirrors-local-msk-ubuntu</a></b>.<br><br>
3. To be implemented: Update symlink pointed to last stable version of Ubuntu upstream mirror if tests successfull.<br><br>
See build description of last successful build here or for <b><a href="/job/{version-id}.set_ubuntu_upstream_mirror/">{version-id}.set_ubuntu_upstream_mirror</a></b>
for information about last stable mirror version.<br><br>

